INT. KITCHEN - NIGHT

= Jane finds Max raiding the fridge again.

JANE leans in the doorway, arms folded.

JANE
You said you'd stop doing this.

MAX
(without turning)
Doing what?

JANE
The midnight thing.

MAX freezes, holding a yogurt.

MAX
This is a snack.

[[Could move this beat earlier in the act.]]

JANE
That's the third "snack" tonight.
